  <h1>Age Difference Calculator</h1>
  <p class="page-desc">Enter two birthdays to find the exact age difference in years, months, and days, plus each person's current age and the "half your age plus 7" rule result.</p>

  <div class="calculator-box">
    <div class="calc-inputs">
